---
// src/components/GrowthEngine.astro
---
<section id="tech" class="py-24 bg-slate-900 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[url('/grid.svg')] opacity-[0.05]"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-blue-600/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-cyan-500/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
        
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight text-display">
                The Engine That Makes You <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-400">Unmissable on Google</span>.
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl font-normal leading-relaxed">
                We don't just build a website. We turn your core service into a programmatic keyword net that captures traffic from every town in your area.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-24">
            
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center relative z-20">
                <div class="w-72 bg-slate-800/80 backdrop-blur-md border-2 border-blue-500 shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(59,130,246,0.3)] rounded-2xl p-6 text-center relative overflow-hidden group">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-500/10 animate-pulse"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white mb-3 shadow-lg">
                            <i data-lucide="database" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-300 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Your Core Service Input</span>
                        <div class="text-xl font-bold text-white">"House Renovation"</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative h-32 flex flex-col items-center justify-center -mt-2 -mb-2 z-10">
                <div class="w-1 h-1/2 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-500 via-cyan-400 to-cyan-500 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(34,211,238,0.5)]"></div>
                
                <div class="relative z-20 bg-slate-900 border border-cyan-500 text-cyan-400 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(6,182,212,0.4)] flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i data-lucide="share-2" class="w-3 h-3 animate-spin-slow"></i>
                    Stegg Multiplier
                </div>

                <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-[50%] left-[16%] right-[16%] h-8 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-r-2 border-cyan-500/50 rounded-t-3xl mt-4"></div>
                
                <div class="hidden md:flex w-full justify-between max-w-[85%] mt-auto px-[8%]">
                    <div class="w-0.5 h-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-cyan-500/50 to-transparent"></div>
                    <div class="w-0.5 h-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-cyan-500/50 to-transparent"></div>
                    <div class="w-0.5 h-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-cyan-500/50 to-transparent"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 relative z-20">
                
                <div class="bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-blue-900/20 transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300 border border-slate-200">
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-100 p-3">
                        <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-full py-1.5 px-3 flex items-center gap-2 shadow-sm">
                            <i data-lucide="search" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-slate-400"></i>
                            <span class="text-xs text-slate-600 truncate">renovation contractor <strong>bangsar</strong></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 mb-1">
                            <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-full p-1"><img src="/favicon.svg" class="w-3 h-3 block opacity-50"></div>
                            <div class="flex flex-col">
                                <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-900 leading-none">YourBusiness.</span>
                                <span class="text-[9px] text-green-700 leading-none">YourBusiness.co › services › bangsar</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-[#1a0dab] text-sm font-medium leading-snug hover:underline cursor-pointer mb-1">
                            No.1 House Renovation Contractor in <strong>Bangsar</strong>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                            Looking for trusted renovators in Jalan Telawi area? We specialize in terrace and condo renovations...
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-blue-900/20 transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300 border border-slate-200">
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-100 p-3">
                        <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-full py-1.5 px-3 flex items-center gap-2 shadow-sm">
                            <i data-lucide="search" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-slate-400"></i>
                            <span class="text-xs text-slate-600 truncate">affordable kitchen cabinet <strong>damansara</strong></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 mb-1">
                            <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-full p-1"><img src="/favicon.svg" class="w-3 h-3 block opacity-50"></div>
                            <div class="flex flex-col">
                                <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-900 leading-none">YourBusiness.</span>
                                <span class="text-[9px] text-green-700 leading-none">YourBusiness.co › services › damansara</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-[#1a0dab] text-sm font-medium leading-snug hover:underline cursor-pointer mb-1">
                            Best Kitchen Cabinet Deals in <strong>Damansara Heights</strong>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                            Servicing Damansara Heights, Bukit Damansara and surrounding areas with premium materials...
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative group">
                    <div class="absolute top-2 left-2 w-full h-full bg-white rounded-xl opacity-40 scale-[0.98] border border-slate-200 z-0"></div>
                    <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 w-full h-full bg-white rounded-xl opacity-20 scale-[0.96] border border-slate-200 z-0"></div>

                    <div class="relative z-10 bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-blue-900/20 transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300 border border-slate-200 h-full flex flex-col">
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-100 p-3">
                            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-full py-1.5 px-3 flex items-center gap-2 shadow-sm">
                                <i data-lucide="search" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-slate-400"></i>
                                <span class="text-xs text-slate-600 truncate">plumbing services <strong>cheras</strong></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-4 flex-grow">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 mb-1">
                                <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-full p-1"><img src="/favicon.svg" class="w-3 h-3 block opacity-50"></div>
                                <div class="flex flex-col">
                                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-900 leading-none">YourBusiness.</span>
                                    <span class="text-[9px] text-green-700 leading-none">YourBusiness.co › services › cheras</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-[#1a0dab] text-sm font-medium leading-snug hover:underline cursor-pointer mb-1">
                                Emergency Plumbing Services <strong>Cheras</strong>
                            </h3>
                            <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-dashed border-slate-200">
                                <div class="bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold flex items-center gap-2">
                                    <i data-lucide="plus-circle" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                                    ...and ranking for 50+ more neighborhoods.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-slate-800 pt-16">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                
                <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-yellow-400 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                        <i data-lucide="zap" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Google-Preferred Speed</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        We code in <strong>Astro & Next.js</strong>—the same tech used by Netflix. Your site loads instantly, which Google rewards with higher rankings.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-900/50 to-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-2xl border border-blue-500/30 hover:border-blue-500 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 group relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-500/5 group-hover:bg-blue-500/10 transition-colors"></div>
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-white group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform relative z-10">
                        <i data-lucide="network" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 relative z-10">The 800-Page Army</h3>
                    <p class="text-blue-100/80 text-sm leading-relaxed relative z-10">
                        While competitors build 5 pages, we deploy <strong>800+ targeted landing pages</strong>. We cover every service in every neighborhood, capturing leads others miss.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 hover:border-green-500/50 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-green-400 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                        <i data-lucide="mouse-pointer-click" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Conversion Focused</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Traffic is useless without sales. We engineer psychological triggers and high-value CTAs that turn casual browsers into paying appointments.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>